For all designs I ask you to make, have them be beautiful, not cookie cutter. Make webpages that are fully featured and worthy for production. 
Always look to construct rather than destruct when making any changes, do prioritize change over 
deletion. 

By default, this template supports JSX syntax with Tailwind CSS classes, React hooks, and Lucide React for icons. Do not install other packages for UI themes, icons, etc unless absolutely necessary or I request them.

Use icons from lucide-react for logos.

Always double check if there are going to be negative repercusions of the app functionality when 
applying a change; in that case ask me first. 

We are trying to give a nice comprehensive service to our customers. This app should be at the 
very top of quality and nice solutions for fleet management, from the smallest fleet ot the 
biggest